Descriptions: A man is fixing the buttons on his plaid shirt while sitting on a couch in front of a coffee table
A man is reading the back cover of a book at a coffee table while sitting on a couch
A man is preparing to throw a pillow while sitting on a couch
A group of a few people are playing with a soccer ball on a grass field
A woman hit a man's bike and they are discussing the situation. The bike is knocked over on the street, and the man looks upset
A man is doing homework at a table while sitting on a couch.
A man is tossing a ball at a tower of balanced bottles, aiming to knock them over.
A man is writing on a small piece of paper, presumably to fold and add to the bowl of folded paper, maybe to create a random pool to draw from.
A man is sitting on a couch while trying to fix a broken flashlight
A man is holding a glass and a bottle cap on a couch
A man is cleaning an outdoor lunchtable while two people chat at another nearby table.
A man is using a chair to climb down after retrieving a wine glass from an overhead cupboard.
A man is folding laundry in his living room.
A man appears to be robbing to people using a knife to threaten them. The people have a small backpack and an apple they have cut up.

A man is looking for a ball that has rolled beneath a couch.
